trans-unit.source: Provides methods for writing <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> objects to [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_metro](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-metro-md.md)] documents or to a print queue in batch mode.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller metoder för att skriva <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> objekt till [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_metro](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-metro-md.md)] dokument eller till en utskriftskö i batch-läge.

trans-unit.source: Because this class has no constructor, use the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.CreateVisualsCollator%2A> method to create an instance.
trans-unit.target: Eftersom den här klassen har ingen konstruktor, använda den <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.CreateVisualsCollator%2A>metoden för att skapa en instans.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.CreateVisualsCollator%2A>

trans-unit.source: The VisualsToXpsDocument writes to the same target <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> or <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> as the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter> that creates the VisualsToXpsDocument.
trans-unit.target: VisualsToXpsDocument skriver till samma mål <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>eller <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>som den <xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter>som skapar VisualsToXpsDocument.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual> becomes a page in the document.
trans-unit.target: Varje <xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual>blir en sida i dokumentet.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual>

trans-unit.source: Indicates that write operations can begin.
trans-unit.target: Anger att skrivåtgärder kan börja.

trans-unit.source: You must call this method before you call any <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.Write%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.WriteAsync%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Du måste anropa den här metoden innan du anropar någon <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.Write%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.WriteAsync%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.WriteAsync%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.Write%2A>

trans-unit.source: After the last write operation, call <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.EndBatchWrite%2A>.
trans-unit.target: När sist skrivåtgärd, anropa <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.EndBatchWrite%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.EndBatchWrite%2A>

trans-unit.source: Cancels a synchronous writing operation.
trans-unit.target: Avbryter en synkron skrivning-åtgärden.

trans-unit.source: For example, an exception is thrown if the Cancel method is called and a writing operation is not in progress.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel undantag ett om Cancel-metoden anropas och en skrivning pågår inte.

trans-unit.source: The state of the <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument"></xref> is not compatible with a Cancel operation.
trans-unit.target: Tillståndet för den <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument"> </xref> är inte kompatibel med en åtgärd för att avbryta.

trans-unit.source: Cancels an asynchronous writing operation.
trans-unit.target: Avbryter en asynkron skrivning-åtgärden.

trans-unit.source: For example, an exception is thrown if the CancelAsync method is called and a writing operation is not in progress.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel undantag ett om CancelAsync-metoden anropas och en skrivning pågår inte.

trans-unit.source: The state of the <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument"></xref> is not compatible with a CancelAsync operation.
trans-unit.target: Tillståndet för den <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument"> </xref> är inte kompatibel med en CancelAsync-åtgärd.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that write operations must end.
trans-unit.target: Anger att skrivåtgärder måste avslutas.

trans-unit.source: After the last call to <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.Write%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.WriteAsync%2A>, call this method.
trans-unit.target: Efter det senaste anropet till <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.Write%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.WriteAsync%2A>, anropa den här metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.WriteAsync%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.Write%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must call <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.BeginBatchWrite%2A> before any write operations.
trans-unit.target: Du måste anropa <xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.BeginBatchWrite%2A>innan någon skrivåtgärder.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.VisualsToXpsDocument.BeginBatchWrite%2A>

trans-unit.source: Writes a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> synchronously to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref> or a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> synkront till en <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref> eller en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> that is written.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> som skrivs.

trans-unit.source: Writes a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> synchronously to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref> or a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref> and includes a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> synkront till en <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref> eller en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref> och innehåller en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method does not validate or modify the specified `printTicket` for a particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden inte verifiera eller ändra den angivna `printTicket` för en viss <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: If necessary, use the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A> method to create a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> that is specific to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> and is valid for a specified printer.
trans-unit.target: Om du använder den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>metoden för att skapa en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>som är specifika för den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>och är giltigt för en angiven skrivare.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> that is written.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> som skrivs.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that represents the default printing preferences for the document.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> som representerar standardinställningarna för dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: Writes a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> asynchronously to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref> or a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> asynkront till en <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref> eller en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> that is written.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> som skrivs.

trans-unit.source: Writes a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> asynchronously to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref> or a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref> and includes additional information that the caller wants to pass to an event handler.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> asynkront till en <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref> eller en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref> och innehåller ytterligare information som anroparen vill skicka till en händelsehanterare.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> that is written.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> som skrivs.

trans-unit.source: An object that contains data that the caller wants to pass to the <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.WritingCompleted"></xref> event handler.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt som innehåller data som anroparen vill skicka till den <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.WritingCompleted"> </xref> händelsehanterare.

trans-unit.source: Writes a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> asynchronously to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref> or a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref> and includes a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> asynkront till en <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref> eller en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref> och innehåller en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method does not validate or modify the specified `printTicket` for a particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden inte verifiera eller ändra den angivna `printTicket` för en viss <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: If necessary, use the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A> method to create a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> that is specific to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> and is valid for a specified printer.
trans-unit.target: Om du använder den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>metoden för att skapa en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>som är specifika för den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>och är giltigt för en angiven skrivare.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> that is written.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> som skrivs.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that represents the default printing preferences for the document.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> som representerar standardinställningarna för dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: Writes a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> asynchronously to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref> or a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref>; also includes a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> and any additional information that the caller wants to pass to an event handler.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> asynkront till en <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref> eller en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref>; innehåller också en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> och eventuell ytterligare information som anroparen vill skicka till en händelsehanterare.

trans-unit.source: This method does not validate or modify the specified `printTicket` for a particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden inte verifiera eller ändra den angivna `printTicket` för en viss <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: If necessary, use the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A> method to create a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> that is specific to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> and is valid for a specified printer.
trans-unit.target: Om du använder den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>metoden för att skapa en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>som är specifika för den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>och är giltigt för en angiven skrivare.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"></xref> that is written.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Visual"> </xref> som skrivs.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that represents the default printing preferences for the document.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> som representerar standardinställningarna för dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: An object that contains the data that the caller wants to pass to the <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.WritingCompleted"></xref> event handler.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt som innehåller de data som anroparen vill skicka till den <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.XpsDocumentWriter.WritingCompleted"> </xref> händelsehanterare.
